MILITARY CONTEXT AND SECURITY

Authorized Use:
- This Software is designed exclusively for administrative management of Military Organizations
- Use is restricted to authorized military personnel and approved contractors
- The Software handles administrative data only - not operational or classified information

Security Requirements:
- Users must maintain appropriate security clearance as required by their organization
- All deployments must follow military cybersecurity standards
- Access must be controlled through proper authentication mechanisms
- Data must be protected according to military data classification guidelines

Prohibited Military Uses:
This Software shall NOT be used for:
- Operational military planning or execution
- Classified information management
- Weapons systems integration
- Tactical communications
- Intelligence operations
- Command and control systems

DATA AND PRIVACY

Data Ownership:
- All data entered into the Software remains the property of the respective Military Organization
- The Licensor claims no ownership rights over user data
- Users are responsible for data classification and protection

Data Security:
- Users must implement appropriate security measures for data protection
- Regular backups and disaster recovery procedures are the user's responsibility
- Data encryption and access controls must be maintained according to military standards

Privacy Compliance:
- Users must ensure compliance with applicable privacy regulations
- Personal data of military personnel must be handled according to military privacy policies
- Data retention policies must align with military record-keeping requirements

